Welcome to PARL Duo's Privacy Policy, where we're committed to
safeguarding your privacy with transparency, security, and clarity. Let's dive
into the nitty-gritty details:
Account Setup:
When you create an account with PARL Duo, we collect the following
information to get you started:
 Email address
 Secure password
 Unique user ID
 Optional profile picture
Messenger Magic:
As you engage with our messenger, we collect additional data to enhance
your experience:
 Messages & Attachments: Your conversations, including voice
messages and attachments, are securely stored in our databases.
 Account Details: Your profile picture and user ID are associated with
each message to personalize your interactions.
 Date & Time: We timestamp each message to maintain chronological
order within your chats.
PARL Duo
Your Privacy, Our Priority
Legal Collections:
In rare cases of policy violations, we may need to collect additional information to
address the issue effectively. Rest assured, your privacy remains our top priority.
2. Data Security: Our Commitment to Protection
We take data security seriously and implement robust measures to ensure
your information remains safe and secure:
 Encryption: Your data is encrypted using state-of-the-art technology to
prevent unauthorized access.
 E2EE Messaging: Our messenger features end-to-end encryption,
ensuring that only you and your intended recipient can access your
messages.
3. Your Choices: Empowering Your Experience
At PARL Duo, we believe in empowering users to control their own data:
 Account Preferences: You have full control over your account settings,
including password changes, profile updates, and subscription
adjustments.
 Opt-Out Options: You can choose to delete your account or cancel your
subscription at any time.
4. Policy Updates: Staying Current
Our privacy policy is a living document that evolves with industry standards
and user feedback:
 Updates: Any changes to our privacy policy will be communicated to
users through the app and posted on our website.
5. Connect with Us: Your Feedback Matters
We're here to address any questions or concerns you may have regarding our
privacy practices:
 Contact Information: You can reach out to us at
parl.feedbacks@gmail.com for assistance or clarification.
